# ── AI assistant ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Anthropic API key for the grounded portfolio assistant (server-side only —
# never exposed to the browser). Without it, the /api/chat endpoint falls back
# to a deterministic, still-grounded canned answer so the site keeps working.
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# Optional: override the Claude model the assistant uses. Defaults to
# claude-opus-4-8. For a faster / cheaper assistant set this to
# claude-haiku-4-5 (this is a simple grounded Q&A use case).
CLAUDE_MODEL=claude-opus-4-8
